    ],
    "http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#wasDerivedFrom": [
      {
        "@id": "https://ww1.ticketpro.ca/event.php?event_id=7382"
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/url": [
      {
        "@id": "https://ww1.ticketpro.ca/event.php?event_id=7382"
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/name": [
      {
        "@value": "Un soir ensemble"
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/description": [
      {
        "@value": "<p>In <b><i>Un soir ensemble</i></b>, these two up-and-coming singer-songwriters celebrate friendship in all its forms. Alternating between covers of Quebec song classics and original compositions, the two friends treat you to a thoroughly enjoyable evening, set against a surprising theatrical backdrop and rich staging. No pleasure will be spared!</p>\n\n<p>Both modern and classic, <b>Émile Bourgault</b> commands the stage with a moving abandon. He is very much a product of his time, yet he knows his roots and has carved out his place in a lineage stretching <b>from Ferland to Philippe B</b>. Oscillating between art songs and catchy pop tunes, he demonstrates a keen sense of showmanship and a constant attention to the right word. His debut album, Tant mieux, released in the spring of 2024 and produced by Félix Dyotte (Pierre Lapointe, Évelyne Brochu), earned him a nomination at the ADISQ Gala in the New Artist of the Year category.</p>\n\n<p>From a very young age, <b>Louis-Julien Durso</b>'s passion for <b>music and comedy</b> has never waned. A versatile artist, he has gained extensive experience both on camera and on stage, whether in the sitcom Ces gars-là or alongside renowned comedians such as <b>François Morency, Pierre Verville, and André-Philippe Gagnon</b>. Active behind the microphone, he also lends his voice to Hollywood productions as a voice actor. A tireless creator, Louis-Julien now devotes every day to writing his own concepts and routines, refining an artistic voice that is already unique and promising.</p>\n\n\n<style>\n@media screen and (max-width: 600px){\niframe{width:100%;}\n}\ntw-seats-selectes-plv{display: none !important;}\n</style>"
      }
    ],
