    ],
    "http://schema.org/description": [
      {
        "@value": "<p>Vishal Dadlani and Shekhar Ravjiani form one of Bollywood's most popular music\ncomposer duos, known as Vishal-Shekhar. They are famous for creating\nenergetic, modern, and chart-topping songs in Hindi cinema.<br><br>\n\nA composer, singer, and producer duo in the Indian music industry<br>\n• Active since the early 2000s<br>\n• Known for blending Bollywood melodies with pop, electronic, rock, and\ninternational sounds</p>\n<style>\n@media screen and (max-width: 600px){iframe{width:100%;}}\n.tw-seats-selectes-plv {display: none;}\ntw-seats-selectes-plv{display: none !important;}\n</style>"
